'''阿尔伯特·“阿尔”·格林尼'''（{{lang|en|Albert "Al" Greene}}，{{bd|1946年|4月13日|}}）是一位美国歌手，在1970年代早期有多首[[灵魂乐|灵魂乐]]歌曲在榜单上取得佳绩，包括《{{lang|en|Tired of Being Alone}}》、《{{lang|en|I'm Still In Love With You}}》、《{{lang|en|Love and Happiness}}》和他的代表作《{{lang|en|Let's Stay Together}}》。他被称为“最后一位伟大的灵魂乐歌手”<ref>{{cite web |author=Zak Smith |url=http://thecelebritycafe.com/feature/2014/01/10-greatest-al-green-songs |title=The 10 Greatest Al Green Songs |publisher=TheCelebrityCafe.com |date=2014-01-22 |accessdate=2014-04-18 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140304121419/http://thecelebritycafe.com/feature/2014/01/10-greatest-al-green-songs |archivedate=2014-03-04 }}</ref><ref>{{cite book|url=http://books.google.com/books?id=o552g5xRRiwC&pg=PA285&lpg=PA285&dq=al+green+the+last+of+the+great+soul+singers&source=bl&ots=z6n1jRqpqh&sig=ingo0uNm7_6SEZG2aKL69uyYd18&hl=en&sa=X&ei=c9gQU9_4FcXzoATPrIBI&ved=0CFAQ6AEwBQ#v=onepage&q=al%20green%20the%20last%20of%20the%20great%20soul%20singers&f=false |title=All Music Guide to Soul: The Definitive Guide to R&B and Soul - Google Books |publisher=Books.google.com |date= |accessdate=2014-04-18}}</ref>，于1995年被选入[[摇滚名人堂|摇滚名人堂]]<ref name=hall>{{cite web|url=http://www.rockhall.com/inductees/al-green|title=Al Green|publisher=[[Rock_and_Roll_Hall_of_Fame|Rock and Roll Hall of Fame]]}}</ref>，在《[[滚石_(杂志)|滚石]]》杂志“史上最伟大的100位艺人”榜单上排名第66位。

